Feature: DataGridSample

#Sheet: AddTwoNumbers
Scenario: Add two numbers

Given I have following two numbers  
 | First Number | Second Number  |
 | 50			| 70			 |
When the two numbers are added
Then the result should be 120

#Sheet: HavingMinusFormulaInTable
Scenario: Having minus formula in table

Given I have following two numbers  
 | First Number | Second Number  |
 | 1.1			| 70			 |
When the two numbers are added
Then the result should be 71.1

#Sheet: SumProduct
Scenario: SumProduct Function  
   
Given I have following list of numbers  
 | First Number | Second Number  |
 | 50			| 70  |
 | 4.3			 | 12  |
 | -3			 | 11  |
   
When I call the SumProduct function  
   
Then the result should be 3518.6 

#Sheet: SumAverage
Scenario: SumAverage Function 
# To test that table value will not be ignored due to empty space 
# For simplify testing purpose, I made the roll average full integer. 
Given I have following list of numbers 
| First Number | Second Number | Third Number | Forth Number |
|           50 |            70 |          100 |           20 |
|              |            12 |            4 |              |
|           -3 |               |              |           11 |
|              |               |           24 |           20 |
When I call the SumAverage function 
Then the result should be 94 
